R12B is H; C1-C6 alkyl; (C1-C3 alkoxy)C2-C6 alkyl; (hydroxy)C2-C6 alkyl; (R13BR14BN)C2-C6 alkyl; (R13BR14BNOC)C1-C6 alkyl; CONR13BR14B; CSNR13BR14B; or C(NH)NR13BR14B; and
